    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I make the most of my R400 entrance by eating everything that I see. I take many things and stash them in the bag for later. We eat dinner watching university netball on the TV. The bar is open and unattended so we decide to do a whiskey tasting with their entire range. Bells is initially the best - but upon revisiting lacks the beautiful smoky flavour that it had on the first sip. ",
            "link": null
          },
